{
  "name": "Water Release Water Palm Blade",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Water.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You generate two blades of chakra enhanced water over your hands that you launch in an arc. Make a ranged Ninjutsu Attack dealing 4d8 Cold damage on a hit.</p><p>A creature affected by this jutsu becomes sheathed in vibrating water until the start of your next turn. If the target moves or is moved at least 5 feet before the start of your next turn, it explodes, dealing 1d6 cold damage to the affected creature and all creatures of your choice within 5 feet of the original target.</p><p>If used near a sufficient source of water, reduce the chakra cost of this jutsu by 2 or increase the damage of the attack by 1 die.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the damage of this jutsu by 1d8.</p>",
